$interpreted: Prison Guard: All of you! You'd best know your place and not cause any problems.
Death Row Prisoner: Wahaha! You wussies afraid of the cold? There's plenty of space, why is everyone crowding in over here?
Death Row Prisoner: No!? You aren't afraid of that human, are you...!?
Lizard Thug: If you're such a tough guy, why don't you go see for yourself?
Death Row Prisoner: Hmph! You think I'm scared?
Thief: We're waiting, tough guy.
Death Row Prisoner: Ha! I don't know how many guys like this I've killed!
Thief: But he—
Death Row Prisoner: I don't care!!!
Death Row Prisoner: *spit*...you wussies are a disgrace to lizards!
Death Row Prisoner: Hey buddy, get outta my way!
Lazer: ......
Death Row Prisoner: Are you deaf!? You listen when I'm talking to you!
Lazer: ......
Lizard Thug: Hehe, you think you're a tough guy, do you? I don't give a rat's tush!
Death Row Prisoner: Time to die scumbag!!
Lazer: ......
Death Row Prisoner: I give up!! I give up!!
Lizard Thug: Hey, you thought you were gonna beat that guy to a pulp?
Lizard Thug: He's the only one who has ever gotten out of the Colosseum alive. Plus, he completely destroyed the bounty hunters sent to capture him.
Death Row Prisoner: Are you...you mean to tell me that's the infamous - - Lazer Bernard!?
Prison Guard: What are you doing!? All of you, break it up!
Prison Guard: Bernard! Let'em go! Didn't I tell you not to touch anyone?
Lazer: The worms were squealing, I was just shutting them up, that's all.
Prison Guard: You little....!
Prison Guard II: The nobles and the High Priest are arriving!
Prison Guard II: The battle is about to begin. Everybody, prepare yourself.
Prison Guard: No one has ever gotten out of the Colosseum alive. When I collect your corpse, we'll see if you're still this arrogant!
Prison Guard: SCUM! You all deserve to die. Now choose your weapon. Your fate lies in the Colosseum.
Death Row Prisoner: I-I'm sorry for that back there...I didn't know you were Lazer Bernard. I deserved that.
Death Row Prisoner: While we're in the Colosseum, could you...spare me some mercy?
Lazer: Fine. I won't touch you in there.
Death Row Prisoner: Oh, thank God! Thank you, thank you...
Death Row Prisoner: Ahhhh!!!! My eye!!!!!!!!!
Lazer: I won't touch you, since you won't have the chance to get inside.
Death Row Prisoner: You...piece of fecal matter!!!
Lazer: Looks like you've run out of luck. Choose your weapon.
Lazer: ...To see you once more, I'd do anything.
Lazer: Wait for me, my Mirage.
